OL,3,COne punch killer's mum jailed after
OL,4,Ctrying to stop police getting his phone
OL,6,FThe mother of a one punch killer has
OL,7,Fbeen jailed after trying to prevent
OL,8,Fpolice officers from accessing her
OL,9,Fson's phone.
OL,11,FScott Akester, 31, died in hospital
OL,12,Fafter a single-punch attack on a night
OL,13,Fout in in November 2022.
OL,15,FMichael Pearson, now 31, was jailed
OL,16,Ffor more than seven years after being
OL,17,Ffound guilty of manslaughter.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/18
