OL,3,COne punch killer's mum jailed after
OL,4,Ctrying to stop police getting his phone
OL,6,FRobert Stevenson, prosecuting, said
OL,7,Fthat, after the attack, Michael
OL,8,FPearson texted his girlfriend, friends
OL,9,Fand brother about what happened to Mr
OL,10,FAkester.
OL,12,FHis brother had been on the night out
OL,13,Fand was there at the time of the
OL,14,Fassault. Michael Pearson suggested
OL,15,Fthat Mr Akester "had it coming"
OL,16,Fbecause of a falling out with
OL,17,FMichael's brother during the evening.
OL,19,FHe said in messages that he "sparked
OL,20,Fhim out" and that Mr Akester's head
OL,21,Fhit the ground very hard.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/18
