OL,3,COne punch killer's mum jailed after
OL,4,Ctrying to stop police getting his phone
OL,6,FHe was panicking about a couple who
OL,7,Fhad been close to the assault because
OL,8,Fthey might be possible witnesses. He
OL,9,Ftold his girlfriend, brother and
OL,10,Ffriends to delete their text messages.
OL,12,FShortly before handing himself in,
OL,13,FMichael Pearson made Google searches
OL,14,Fabout the likely sentence for
OL,15,Fmanslaughter.
OL,17,FMr Stevenson said: "It was obvious
OL,18,Fthat his phone was going to be of
OL,19,Fconsiderable assistance in the
OL,20,Finvestigation."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/18
