OL,3,COne punch killer's mum jailed after
OL,4,Ctrying to stop police getting his phone
OL,6,FShe was wearing a dressing gown and
OL,7,Fshe was allowed to get changed. She
OL,8,Fput on a coat and the broken phone of
OL,9,FMichael Pearson was in the pocket. She
OL,10,Fsaid that she needed the toilet twice
OL,11,Fin quick succession.
OL,13,FShe took off the coat with the broken
OL,14,Fphone in the pocket and she put it on
OL,15,Fher bed. She put on a different coat
OL,16,Fbefore she was searched and taken into
OL,17,Fcustody.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/18
