OL,3,COne punch killer's mum jailed after
OL,4,Ctrying to stop police getting his phone
OL,6,FShe made no comment during police
OL,7,Finterview to all questions but said in
OL,8,Fa statement that she had no idea where
OL,9,FMichael Pearson's phone was.
OL,11,F"The phone was of significant
OL,12,Fimportance during the trial of Michael
OL,13,FPearson," said Mr Stevenson.
OL,15,FWhen police found the phone at Joanne
OL,16,FPearson's home, in her coat pocket, it
OL,17,Fwas in a plastic bag and had been
OL,18,Fsmashed and doused in acetone or a
OL,19,Fsimilar liquid.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/18
