OL,3,COne punch killer's mum jailed after
OL,4,Ctrying to stop police getting his phone
OL,6,F"The prosecution can't say when the
OL,7,Fphone was destroyed," said Mr
OL,8,FStevenson. It was during the afternoon
OL,9,For evening of November 19, at a time
OL,10,Fwhen Mr Akester was gravely ill.
OL,12,FJoanne Pearson, a 61-year-old retired
OL,13,Fsocial worker, admitted committing an
OL,14,Fact with intent to pervert the course
OL,15,Fof justice.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/18
