OL,3,COne punch killer's mum jailed after
OL,4,Ctrying to stop police getting his phone
OL,6,FCharlotte Baines, mitigating, said
OL,7,Fthat Joanne Pearson had no previous
OL,8,Fconvictions. At the time, she was
OL,9,F"somewhat in a state of emotional
OL,10,Fturmoil" but she understood the impact
OL,11,Fof Mr Akester's death on his family
OL,12,Fand friends.
OL,14,F"She has shown exceptional victim
OL,15,Fempathy," said Miss Baines. "She feels
OL,16,Fdreadfully sympathetic and sorrowful
OL,17,Ffor their loss. She was going through
OL,18,Fsome emotional turmoil and she let a
OL,19,Fvery strong misguided loyalty take
OL,20,Fover her that day."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/18
