OL,3,COne punch killer's mum jailed after
OL,4,Ctrying to stop police getting his phone
OL,6,FJoanne Pearson did not know what
OL,7,Fmaterial was on the phone. "That
OL,8,Flessens the seriousness of the
OL,9,Foffence," said Miss Baines. At the
OL,10,Ftime, Mr Akester had not died but
OL,11,FJoanne Pearson knew that he was
OL,12,Fgravely ill at that time.
OL,14,F"The police did have to get over some
OL,15,Fhurdles in order to obtain the
OL,16,Fmaterial," said Miss Baines.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/18
