OL,3,COne punch killer's mum jailed after
OL,4,Ctrying to stop police getting his phone
OL,6,FThere were numerous character
OL,7,Freferences for her. She started as a
OL,8,Fnursery nurse before retraining,
OL,9,Fgraduating from Hull University and
OL,10,Fbecoming a social worker, with a
OL,11,Fmanagerial role in safeguarding
OL,12,Fchildren.
OL,14,FShe retired in 2021 after 20 years in
OL,15,Fthat sort of work and she helped to
OL,16,Flook after Michael Pearson's two
OL,17,Fchildren, aged four and two.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/18
