OL,3,COne punch killer's mum jailed after
OL,4,Ctrying to stop police getting his phone
OL,6,FJudge John Thackray KC told Pearson:
OL,7,F"You knew that your son was involved
OL,8,Fin assaulting his friend and you
OL,9,Fappreciated the significance of your
OL,10,Fson's mobile telephone. It was a
OL,11,Fcritically important piece of evidence.
OL,13,F"It contained important bad character
OL,14,Fevidence but, perhaps most
OL,15,Fimportantly, the contents demonstrated
OL,16,Fthat your son's actions were unlawful
OL,17,Fand contrary to self-defence.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G14/18
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
