PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F367A1715696868
OL,3,COne punch killer's mum jailed after
OL,4,Ctrying to stop police getting his phone
OL,6,F"Despite that, having left your son at
OL,7,Fthe police station, you damaged the
OL,8,Ftelephone and did your best to keep it
OL,9,Ffrom the police. It caused significant
OL,10,Fdelays in the investigation and that
OL,11,Fculminated in an application to vacate
OL,12,Fyour son's trial only three days
OL,13,Fbefore the trial was due to commence.
OL,15,F"I rejected that application but I
OL,16,Fhave no doubt that the application
OL,17,Fitself caused distress and concern to
OL,18,Fthe family of Scott Akester. I accept
OL,19,Fthat you were in a state of turmoil.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G15/18
