OL,3,COne punch killer's mum jailed after
OL,4,Ctrying to stop police getting his phone
OL,6,F"Ultimately, only appropriate
OL,7,Fpunishment can be achieved by way of
OL,8,Fan immediate custodial sentence."
OL,10,FPearson nodded to the judge and looked
OL,11,Fdown as she was led out of the secure
OL,12,Fdock to be taken down to the cells.
OL,14,FDuring an earlier hearing before Hull
OL,15,FMagistrates' Court, a previous charge
OL,16,Fagainst Joanne Pearson of assisting an
OL,17,Foffender was withdrawn.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G16/18
