OL,3,COne punch killer's mum jailed after
OL,4,Ctrying to stop police getting his phone
OL,6,FAfter the hearing, the family of Mr
OL,7,FAkester said in a statement: "For our
OL,8,Ffamily, it wasn't about what sentence
OL,9,Fwas going to be given, it was about
OL,10,Fher being accountable for her actions.
OL,12,F"We are now pleased this process has
OL,13,Fnow completed and all the heartache we
OL,14,Fhave had to go through over the last
OL,15,F18 months has come to an end. We will
OL,16,Fnow strive to move forward with our
OL,17,Fcharity, One Punch Hull and East
OL,18,FYorkshire, keeping Scott's memory
OL,19,Falive for years to come.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G17/18
